            <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Æ </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='5415' hidden='true' id='10' story-point-id='13' type-v2='text' w='14052' x='25716' y='48848'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='9'>Global financial crisis period 2008-09 </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='8986' hidden='true' id='11' story-point-id='13' type-v2='text' w='17121' x='11255' y='81336'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Imports steadily increased from the 1990s to the early 2000s, with an average annual growth rate of 7.7%.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='8986' hidden='true' id='14' story-point-id='14' type-v2='text' w='17121' x='56617' y='41129'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>The trade balance from 1992 to 2007 was negative most of the time, indicating that import activity was more dynamic than export activity, which led to the trade deficit.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='12788' hidden='true' id='15' story-point-id='14' type-v2='text' w='17053' x='56685' y='64977'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Australia&apos;s largest trade deficit, approximately $22.02 billion or about -9.25% of total trade, occurred between 2003 and 2004. Subsequently, the deficit grew to around $23.50 billion, accounting for -9.07% of total trade.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='8871' hidden='true' id='16' story-point-id='15' type-v2='text' w='30150' x='14802' y='79839'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>In Australia&apos;s trade history, 2009 marked the most significant drop 11% from 2008 to 2009 in imports. This decline can be linked to various factors, including the global financial crisis (GFC) that started in late 2008</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Change Ratio: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>88%</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Trade Value: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>$200.6B</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='6221' hidden='true' id='17' story-point-id='15' type-v2='text' w='16576' x='27012' y='60138'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Following the Global Financial Crisis (GFC), import activity witnessed a steady increase each year from 2010 to 2015.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='7604' hidden='true' id='18' story-point-id='15' type-v2='text' w='15075' x='30218' y='47465'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>After GFC, import activity in Australia picked up pace, demonstrating consistent growth from 2010 to 2015</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='9447' hidden='true' id='19' story-point-id='16' type-v2='text' w='16985' x='29127' y='45161'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>The financial crisis had a milder impact compared to the previous global crisis. As a result, import activity quickly rebounded, seeing a significant 13% increase from 2016 to 2017 in total value.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='10138' hidden='true' id='20' story-point-id='17' type-v2='text' w='14256' x='31310' y='77189'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Once again, import value in 2020 is decilned 5% due to the impact of COVID-19 but bounce back strongly with 112% and 126% in Y21 and Y2, respectively</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='11290' hidden='true' id='21' story-point-id='17' type-v2='text' w='16371' x='25853' y='27535'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>This recovery is primarily attributed to the Free Trade Agreements (FTAs) signed with Asis countries, which now rank as Australia&apos;s top two-way trading partners.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='14862' hidden='true' id='23' story-point-id='18' type-v2='text' w='9959' x='6412' y='30876'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>During this period, the export value surged from $42.4 billion to $89 billion, marking a remarkable 210% increase over the past decade</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='11636' hidden='true' id='24' story-point-id='19' type-v2='text' w='11119' x='17394' y='28802'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>From 1998 to 2008, Australia&apos;s export activity witnessed its most fluctuating period in its 35-year trading history</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='9677' hidden='true' id='25' story-point-id='19' type-v2='text' w='11460' x='17394' y='76267'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>After the dip in 2002, export values increased steadily every year from 2002 onwards, reaching a peak growth of 132% in 2008</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='10138' hidden='true' id='26' story-point-id='20' type-v2='text' w='16030' x='20805' y='28226'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Despite these fluctuations, Australia&apos;s export performance showed an overall upward trend in the post-GFC period. Export values rose significantly from </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>$196.6B</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'> in 2009 to </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>$390B</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'> in 2019</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='8871' hidden='true' id='27' story-point-id='20' type-v2='text' w='12483' x='75512' y='28341'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>In post-GFC period, export activity was more dynamic, with most periods showing positive trade balance. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='7028' hidden='true' id='29' story-point-id='21' type-v2='text' w='19441' x='18827' y='29839'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>The downturn was caused by global disruptions in supply chains due to COVID-19 restrictions, which closed borders and interrupted established international trade routes.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{38E26A5B-F69F-4D55-8CF2-D2B9CB5B3278}' />
    </dashboard>
